asset.author: Victorinox AG
asset.hookText:
Experience the Night Vision: http://nightvision.victorinox.com/?id=Utube

------------------------------------------

The new edition is subtly designed along very classic Swiss lines, with a round, wide-open dial face and narrower bezel. Traditional codes are respected; there are no superfluous elements, no show-off gadgetry.

The timepiece's pioneering lighting features are seamlessly incorporated into the sleek dial and bracelet design. The fluid crown protectors are echoed on the other side of the broad, 42mm case. The result is an increased dynamism to the design, and a purer aesthetic balance.
